{"tid":1439468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[機場人] 下一步行動！","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T07:47:46.000Z","uid":44557,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9d26661bc8fb9d15eca1990c11d8aa840e2db7ed","tid":1439468,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家好，我地係726機場集會嘅發起人<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n琴日(8/9)中國民航局就對國泰出咗一個「<span style=\"color: red;\">重大航空安全風險警示</span>」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.caacnews.com.cn/1/1/201908/t20190809_1279295_wap.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caacnews.com.cn%2F1%2F1%2F201908%2Ft20190809_1279295_wap.html&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=3633c2da\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.caacnews.com.cn/1/1/201908/t20190809_1279295_wap.html</a><br />\n<br />\n總共有三點，例如要國泰預先將機組人員嘅資料俾中國審批先可以飛，同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禁止所有發過夢嘅空姐機師飛中國或者經過中國領空，甚至係只要支持人地發夢嘅都唔飛得中國</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n據我地了解，受影響嘅航班包括港龍嘅中國航線，而國泰大約<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一半的航班（包括歐美）都要經過中國領空</span></span>。此舉嚴重干預咗國泰作為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港註冊公司</span></span>嘅運作，從而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">侵害香港自由公平貿易港的聲譽同經濟</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，機組人員嘅私人群組已經充斥住大量飛抵中國後被保安人員<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求額外檢查</span></span>嘅傳聞。包括<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">檢查電話內容、檢查行李及上機搜尋違禁品</span></span> (包括航班提供的香港報紙)，大量傳聞即使未被證實已經製造出大量<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">白色恐怖</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連機組人員只係發過夢或者講一句，都會被禁止飛越領空，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工都無得返</span></span>，呢種白色恐佈又何嘗唔係要求自我審查嘅打壓呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日國泰，明日你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日唔企硬，日後一定衰硬<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地完全明白一間國際企業面對此等壓力嘅難處，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋會等國泰回應再決定<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下一步嘅行動升級。</span><br />\n</span></span><br />\n香港人對國泰不離不棄，希望<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國泰都頂住壓力，同香港人共同進退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTG Channel Link: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFH6T-PlbAGcQnvJ9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFH6T-PlbAGcQnvJ9Q&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=1231e2a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFH6T-PlbAGcQnvJ9Q</a>"},{"pid":"16fb90fd8d281bd062513fdcb03a1f9bdeee0bb4","tid":1439468,"uid":44557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"The Civil Aviation Administration of China has issued formal flight safety warning to Cathay Pacific Airways. The requirements are as attached. <br />\n<br />\nUndoubtedly, these requirements have seriously hindered the freedom of speech of the employees in the whole Cathay Pacific group. <br />\n<br />\nThere were more than 3000 employees in the aviation industry who have gone on the strike on 5 August. Further, more than half of the operating flights from the CX group arrive at or pass by the mainland China, and thus, will be affected by the said requirements. <br />\n<br />\nIf these policies are implemented in the aviation industry, it is possible that all other companies in Hong Kong, which have businesses related to China in any form, might also be threatened by the Chinese government in a similar way. As a result, there will be a heavy impact upon the economy in Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\nAs members of the aviation industry, as well as citizens in Hong Kong, we have serious concerns over the unreasonable requirements by the CAAC. We hereby ask the Civil Aviation Department of Hong Kong to issue a formal response and to protect our freedom of speech, whatever it takes."},{"pid":"5b140dd4233fa0227589e6459ec84754e18a9496","tid":1439468,"uid":44557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKqs1fC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKqs1fC.jpg&h=02c68c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit: Mr. Pilot Facebook<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mr.pilot.hk/photos/a.371271896394280/1134898780031584?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmr.pilot.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.371271896394280%2F1134898780031584%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=5a2cb6db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mr.pilot.hk/photos/a.371271896394280/1134898780031584?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a></span>"},{"pid":"0447e10a7121bfd0a736f76ba30efeabae20d5b1","tid":1439468,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:19:15.000Z","msg":"唔建議機場手足入大埔<br />\n但請推比入左大埔嘅人睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">推行動post呀<br />\n推上熱門呀<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"4e23600d58a5731153e80ce479c6690837766d6d","tid":1439468,"uid":152269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91440da0e8ac2304b99a41c3062ae0de7389b08a","tid":1439468,"uid":44557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"517c235db6dab569d7058952aff4be2a16e22a75","tid":1439468,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"既然唔比返<br />\n就罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm